server.template.java

Class JavaTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.template.java.JavaTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Template

    public class JavaTemplate
extends Object
implements Template
    A JavaTemplate is a factory object for obtaining templates for translating a specific ParsedElement object into a Java source code string.
